-03-13/ty-article/.premium/would-a-u-s-arms-embargo-on-israel-really-stop-the-war-in-gaza/0000018e-36c2-d8f9-a98e-7ec381950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加大与真主党高风险敌对行动的赌注</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-ups-the-ante-in-high-risk-hostilities-with-hezbollah/0000018e-3447-da0e-a78f-fc7ff5510000</link><description>以色列国防军进攻行动扩大到黎巴嫩贝卡谷地 — — 以及真主党的强化反应 — — 使双方更接近一场他们试图避免的战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-ups-the-ante-in-high-risk-hostilities-with-hezbollah/0000018e-3447-da0e-a78f-fc7ff5510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成两人死亡；两名以色列人在耶路撒冷附近被刺伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-live/aid-trucks-enter-northern-gaza-from-israel-for-first-time-since-war-on-hamas-broke-out/0000018e-35a6-d9f7-a5ee-f7efeae50000</link><description>哈马斯呼吁西岸巴勒斯坦人向圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺进军，与以色列安全部队对峙 ■ 以色列国防军证实在黎巴嫩南部的一次袭击中打死哈马斯成员 ■ 以色列国防军在约旦河西岸城市杰宁开火，造成两名巴勒斯坦人死亡，另有两人在附近Givat Ze&amp;#39;ev 定居点 ■ 德国批准武装部队向加沙空投援助物资</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-live/aid-trucks-enter-northern-gaza-from-israel-for-first-time-since-war-on-hamas-broke-out/0000018e-35a6-d9f7-a5ee-f7efeae50000</guid></item><item><title>西岸警察局长：大多数关于定居者暴力的投诉都是虚假的，由无政府主义者提出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</link><description>议会小组委员会周二召开会议，讨论“活动人士的煽动活动”。地区警察指挥官指责人权组织“声誉受损”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</guid></item><item><title>“不可逆转的损害”：以色列火山研究所负责人抗议预算削减计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</link><description>火山研究所代理所长什穆埃尔·阿苏林 (Shmuel Assouline) 表示，由于提议的削减，该机构已暂停其活动，他警告说，这将导致该研究所关闭、诉讼和损害、正在申请的专利被取消以及其所拥有的知识产权的损失。国家</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 21:24:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在东耶路撒冷射杀一名向他们发射烟花的 13 岁青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</link><description>据难民营一名居民称，烟花并非针对军官，也不会对他们构成威胁。国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔在回应这一事件时表示，他向警察对事件的处理“致敬”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</guid></item><item><title>新的加沙战争是拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-biden-and-netanyahu-conveniently-blame-each-other-for-their-gaza-war-failures/0000018e-33e4-d9f7-a5ee-f7ef84670000</link><description>传统观点认为，比比与拜登关系的恶化对两位领导人来说都是一个糟糕的发展。但真的是这样吗？在每种情况下，爆发相互批评和指责也是有好处的</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-biden-and-netanyahu-conveniently-blame-each-other-for-their-gaza-war-failures/0000018e-33e4-d9f7-a5ee-f7ef84670000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学停职否认哈马斯性暴力、指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的巴勒斯坦学者</title><link>h