mined/0000018e-327a-d5ad-addf-7e7bca660000</link><description>人权医生组织称以色列军事医疗院的条件——病人一直被戴上镣铐并蒙住眼睛——是“酷刑”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/nameless-shackled-blindfolded-medical-treatment-of-detainees-from-gaza-examined/0000018e-327a-d5ad-addf-7e7bca660000</guid></item><item><title>新研究显示，可可出人意料地以惊人的速度征服了史前美洲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cocoa-always-was-though-not-sure-always-will-be/0000018e-3322-d606-a5ff-7fb706420000</link><description>可可豆于 5,300 多年前在亚马逊地区被驯化，突然之间，杂交品种在整个南美洲北部和中美洲涌现</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cocoa-always-was-though-not-sure-always-will-be/0000018e-3322-d606-a5ff-7fb706420000</guid></item><item><title>应德国要求，以色列将68名巴勒斯坦孤儿从拉法暂时撤离至约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israel-temporarily-evacuates-68-orphans-from-rafah-to-west-bank-at-germanys-request/0000018e-3396-da0e-a78f-ffbeccf30000</link><description>德国驻特拉维夫大使馆表示，疏散的目的是立即使孩子们脱离“严重”危险，并且是暂时的，并不是永久搬迁。以色列国防军是在以色列政府的指示下进行此次行动的</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israel-temporarily-evacuates-68-orphans-from-rafah-to-west-bank-at-germanys-request/0000018e-3396-da0e-a78f-ffbeccf30000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 158 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-158/0000018e-337e-da0e-a78f-ff7e55a60001</link><description>多哈和开罗的停火谈判仍在继续，但卡塔尔外交部表示，“情况很复杂” ■ 黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 100 多枚火箭弹 ■ 据报道，拜登正在考虑对以色列提供进一步的军事援助，条件是这些援助是否会携带在加沙拉法发动大规模攻势 ■ 战争开始 158 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-158/0000018e-337e-da0e-a78f-ff7e55a60001</guid></item><item><title>他们的亲人在哈马斯囚禁期间被杀。他们为拯救他人的生命而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-loved-ones-were-killed-in-captivity-they-call-to-save-others/0000018e-2f41-dcb3-a58f-efc5ddf90000</link><description>他们被绑架的亲属在加沙被杀。但只要还有其他以色列人仍被囚禁，他们的战斗就没有结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-loved-ones-were-killed-in-captivity-they-call-to-save-others/0000018e-2f41-dcb3-a58f-efc5ddf90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准载有200吨食品的援助船从塞浦路斯起航前往加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/aid-ship-with-200-tons-of-food-sets-sail-from-cyprus-to-gaza-after-israels-approval/0000018e-3338-d5ad-addf-7f3918220000</link><description>通过海运运送食物的努力突显了国际社会对人道主义援助卡车系统的不满，该系统导致加沙北部受到严重忽视。这艘船由 Open Arms 和 World Central Kitchen 组织，预计两三天内抵达加沙海岸</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:28:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/aid-ship-with-200-tons-of-food-sets-sail-from-cyprus-to-gaza-after-israels-approval/0000018e-3338-d5ad-addf-7f3918220000</guid></item><item><title>“如果以色列要这样对待人民，那么他们制定回归法还有什么意义呢？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/whats-the-point-of-having-a-law-of-return-if-theyre-going-to-treat-people-like-this/0000018e-2d0d-dbcf-abee-3ddd4d2d0000</link><description>在发给每个前往以色列回返的人的表格上诚实地回答一个人的心理健康史，有时会让移民走上侵入性询问和长期拖延的道路。一名女性的案例终于可以解决这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/whats-the-point-of-having-a-law-of-return-if-theyre-going-to-treat-people-like-this/0000018e-2d0d-dbcf-abee-3ddd4d2d0000</guid></item><item><title>非政府组织起诉丹麦向以色列出售武器，并援引加沙“潜在的种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-12/ty-article/ngos-sue-denmark-over-arms-sales-to-israel-cite-potential-genocide-in-gaza/0000018e-3316-d606-a5ff-7fb760a30000</link><description>参与诉讼的组织之一的秘书长表示，政客们没有采取行动阻止“加沙潜在的种族灭绝”。上个月，荷兰法院下令荷兰禁止向以色列出口所有 F-35 战斗机零部件</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-12/ty-article/ngos-sue-denmark-over-arms-sales-to-israel-cite-potential-genocide-in-gaza/0000018e-3316-d606-a5ff-7fb760a30000</guid></item></channel></rss>